snippet.title: Star Strikers: Galactic Soccer | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1962210?utm_source=trailer

Star Strikers: Galactic Soccer is a beautiful hand-drawn arcade football game, with fast-paced action, unique playfields and crazy characters from all over the universe! Great in single-player, even better with friends.
